&lt;h2 class=&quot;p8i6j01 paragraph&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p8i6j01 paragraph&quot;&gt;As a Senior Frontend Developer (Vue), you will play a key role in building the products that power better residential aged care in Australia, helping providers deliver safer, more connected care. You will join our Platform Engineering team and work closely with colleagues in Canada and Australia, partnering with Clinical, Finance, and Reporting teams to deliver high‑quality, accessible experiences in our AlayaCare Residential product.&lt;/p&gt;
