&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p8i6j01 paragraph&quot;&gt;You will focus on migrating our Resi platform from AngularJS to Vue 3, improving performance, accessibility, and maintainability while contributing to shared component libraries and automated testing. You will work in a modern, AI‑first development environment with a contemporary frontend stack and a cloud‑native backend. If you are excited by solving complex UI challenges in a regulated, mission‑driven space, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Our frontend stack is Vue 3 (3.5), TypeScript, JavaScript (ES6+), Vite, Pinia, PrimeVue, and Cypress, integrating with a&amp;nbsp;backend built on C#, .NET, and MSSQL Server. We run Docker and Kubernetes on AWS, with Git and Azure DevOps in&amp;nbsp;our pipeline, and use Jasper Report and DataDog for reporting and monitoring.&lt;/p&gt;
